            <p>Donated by Anna Hamlin, 1985-1988.</p>
        </acqinfo>
        <processinfo>
            <p>The Music Division processed the collection in 1988. The order as established by the Music Division was maintained. Some contents were never
        processed and required rehousing.</p>
